{
  "id": "62cd35c03dd412001d1e7ced",
  "title": "ビジネスメールのフォーマット",
  "created": 1657615831,
  "updated": 1693995918,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62cd35c03dd412001d1e7ced",
      "text": "ビジネスメールのフォーマット",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615831,
      "updated": 1657615831
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35d77838e300003d38ff",
      "text": "[ビジネスメール]の[フォーマット]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615831,
      "updated": 1657615837
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35df7838e300003d3901",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615838,
      "updated": 1657615838
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35df7838e300003d3902",
      "text": "[Mijinko_SD.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615838,
      "updated": 1657615841
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35e17838e300003d3903",
      "text": "\tわかりそうでちゃんとわかっているわけではない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615841,
      "updated": 1657615856
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd36d47838e300003d390d",
      "text": "\t\tぶっちゃけ送る度に、表現の方法とかを毎回調べている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657616084,
      "updated": 1657616110
    },
    {
      "id": "635bedc3e5172d0000de4c88",
      "text": "\t\t これ[yosider.icon*2]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1666969029,
      "updated": 1666969050
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35f07838e300003d3904",
      "text": "\t構成としてはこんな感じなんだろうか",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615856,
      "updated": 1657615939
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35f77838e300003d3905",
      "text": "\t\t1. 先方の所属と名前",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615862,
      "updated": 1657615889
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd36067838e300003d3906",
      "text": "\t\t2. [挨拶]と[名乗り]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1657615878,
      "updated": 1666960120
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd360d7838e300003d3907",
      "text": "\t\t3. 何かしらの[お礼]、または[謝罪]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1657615884,
      "updated": 1666960124
    },
    {
      "id": "635bedfae5172d0000de4c89",
      "text": "\t\t 草[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1666969084,
      "updated": 1693991128
    },
    {
      "id": "64f8443b5b98c200003c302a",
      "text": "\t\t [謹啓]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693991996,
      "updated": 1693992005
    },
    {
      "id": "64f84d805b98c20000ddc2b7",
      "text": "\t\t  かなり敬意が高いが、そもそもビジネスメールでこれを使って良いか意見がわかれるところ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693994368,
      "updated": 1693994465
    },
    {
      "id": "64f840df5b98c200003c301c",
      "text": "\t\t [拝啓]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693991135,
      "updated": 1693991147
    },
    {
      "id": "64f840f25b98c200003c301d",
      "text": "\t\t [前略]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693991155,
      "updated": 1693991165
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd36277838e300003d3909",
      "text": "\t\t4. 要件",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615911,
      "updated": 1657615926
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd37227838e300003d390e",
      "text": "\t\t\t簡潔でわかりやすく書く",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657616162,
      "updated": 1657616176
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd37257838e300003d390f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t全部に言えるけれど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657616165,
      "updated": 1657616168
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd36527838e300003d390a",
      "text": "\t\t\tお願いする場合は「要求」にならないようにする",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615954,
      "updated": 1657615972
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd365a7838e300003d390b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t相手の選択肢の消さないように心がける",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657615962,
      "updated": 1657616016
    },
    {
      "id": "64f852e35b98c200002d68a3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t[クッション言葉]を入れて当たりをやわらかくする",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693995747,
      "updated": 1693995800
    },
    {
      "id": "64f8533b5b98c200002d68a4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t逆に、穏やかだが、強く要求する書き方も覚えておいたほうがよい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693995836,
      "updated": 1693995918
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd36917838e300003d390c",
      "text": "\t\t5. 締めの礼と挨拶",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1657616017,
      "updated": 1657616068
    },
    {
      "id": "64f8444e5b98c200003c302b",
      "text": "\t\t [敬白]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693992014,
      "updated": 1693992060
    },
    {
      "id": "64f841015b98c200003c301e",
      "text": "\t\t　[敬具]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693991169,
      "updated": 1693991241
    },
    {
      "id": "64f8410b5b98c200003c301f",
      "text": "\t\t　[草々]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1693991179,
      "updated": 1693991243
    },
    {
      "id": "635bee54e5172d0000de4c8a",
      "text": "\t\tわかりやすく具体的なタイトルをつける",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1666969174,
      "updated": 1666969185
    },
    {
      "id": "62cd35d77838e300003d3900",
      "text": "  必要に応じて、[署名]（[シグネチャ]）を入れる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1657615831,
      "updated": 1693991761
    },
    {
      "id": "635beea6e5172d0000de4c8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1666969256,
      "updated": 1666969256
    },
    {
      "id": "635beea6e5172d0000de4c8c",
      "text": "#メール",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1666969256,
      "updated": 1666969258
    },
    {
      "id": "635beea9e5172d0000de4c8d",
